  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Accepted, W-CON-01)",
  "description": "Synthetic adversarial package derived from Morrison COU2. The package records an Accepted decision for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under VAD conditions (Class III, MRL 5). Thirteen credibility factors are assessed; twelve carry structured requiredLevel and achievedLevel integers. One factor — Model form — is documented only through a richly-written qualitative rationale with no structured level data, constituting the W-CON-01 factor-decision inconsistency: the Accepted outcome is not fully grounded in the structured factor evidence.",
